snippet.title: Joy Of Creation : Ignited Collection - Prototype Gameplay Footage #2
snippet.description:
Check out a little bit of prototype footage provided by the developer of Joy of Creation : Ignition Collection. You can follow him on Twitter!

https://twitter.com/nikson_dev/media

Make sure to subscribe to us!

**Please note the game will be titled Joy Of Creation : Ignited Collection and not Ignition.**
